import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'; import classes from './MySizesPopup.module.css'; import Close from '../icons/close.svg' const MySizesPopup = ({ onClose }) => { const [isPopupOpen, setPopupOpen] = useState(false); const popupRef = useRef(null); const openPopup = () => { setPopupOpen(true); }; const closePopup = () => { setPopupOpen(false); }; useEffect(() => { const handleKeyDown = (event) => { if (event.keyCode === 27) { onClose(); } }; const handleClickOutside = (event) => { if (popupRef.current && !popupRef.current.contains(event.target)) { onClose(); } }; document.addEventListener('mousedown', handleClickOutside); document.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown); return () => { document.removeEventListener('mousedown', handleClickOutside); document.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown); }; }, []); return (
